hess, Spoons, Squalamoucho!, Squeaky Francis, ST. Anthony R. Simons, Staci Oelze, Starkast, Ste Leema, Stef Schwartz, Stefan Kreimeier, Stefania Ricco, Stefano, Stefano <br>“ Aerel” Veronesi, Stefano Borri, Stefano Oppo, Stefano Stradaioli, Step Christopher, Stephan Bugaj, Stephanie Ann Bailey, Stephanie Cory, Stephanie Heinz, Stephen D. O’Quinn, Stephen J. Schatzman, Stephen Newman, <br>Stephen O’Brien, Stephen Pilch, Stephen Rosania, Stephen Schnoebelen, Steve Wiklund, Steven Barrett, Steven Behringer, Steven Bocchetto, Steven Collins, Steven J. Zeve, Steven M. Smith, StEvil, Stragliotto Domenico, <br>Stratagemma, Stéphane Delleuze, Suemia Biafore, Sugomori, Suguru OIkawa, Susan Haarman, SusanU, Sydney LaBorgia, Sylvia Short, T Loquvam, T&amp;J McCord, Tabi Walters, Tabitha Goicher, Tad Kelson, Takk, Tammy <br>Tran, Tanya Cooley, Tao - Kraken aps, Tara S., Tarna Allen, Tasena, Tats Rabelink, Taylor Sosa, Teal, Tebra Hansing, Technodromo, Teocadista, Terrance Marpoe, Terry McKelvey, Thalie Ré, Thalsturz, Thasaidon, Thasic, <br>THE Donnie, The Grim Reaper, The Mad Catter, The Mesa Family, Thea Flurry, TheBearIsDriving, Theodore Martinez, TheThingFromOuterSpace, TheTokenDiceGuy, thomas delrue, Thomas Di Bennardo, Thomas <br>Freed, Thomas R. Gould III, Thomas Rye, Tiberio “Master Ronin” Azzarà, TIE, Tiffany Espinosa, Tiffany Hamlin, Tiger Richardson, Tim D. Griffin, Tim Doyle, Tim Hall, Tim Kuehlhorn, Tim Smith, Tim Tang, Tina <br>Alexandersen Solvang, TiTi Navalta, To my son Lasse Wauters, Tobias Belek, Todd (Konton) Hangos, Todd Daugherty, Todd Zircher, Tola Séamestré, Tom Burdak, Tom Kraft, Tomasz Chmielik, Tommaso Oddone, <br>Tommy Smekens, Tommy Toresjö, Tony Fucina, Toyka, Trallalaura, Trash Heap Games, Travis “Novoreaper” Boillat, Travis Carrier, Travis Foster, Travis Hartland, Trent Michels, Trever “Kid Vorpal” Harwell, Trevor J.J. <br>Sherman, Trip Space-Parasite, Triston Thorpe, Troy Ellis, Trust-No-One Games, Tseng, Hua-Jui, Tubby McButters, Tucker Williamson, Turtle, Twila Cotter, Ty Logan Rollins, tyler &amp; melissa, Tyler Braden, Tyler Jones, <br>Tyler Reid, Tyler Scholz, Tyler Spaulding, V . Franklin, Valentina Paggiarin, Valerie Lever, Valerio Lucido, Valerio Votadoro, Valian, Vassiliy Clottes, Vaughn McDonald, Vegar Fristad, Veronica Vandersteenen, Vespero, <br>Vicky Efram, Victor G. Balcazar Moctezuma, Victor J Kinzer, Victoria Baker, Victoria Johnsen, Ville Kugelberg, Vincent Goodlove, VnNxNeAhng, Vorgartezwerg, Víctor Romero, w. David Lewis, Wayne Bridge, Wayne <br>Marshall, Welgian Baffle, Weronika Solarek, Wes Cumbee, Wes Woods, whateley0825, WhimsyWanda, Wicked Thing, Will Godar, Will Phillips, Willem B., William Bonacina, William G Schiemenz, William J. Scott III, <br>William Joseph Bechard, William Z. Cohen  MSGT/USMC, ret., WM. Downs, wookwok, Wren, www.despertalia.com, Wynter Storm, Xavier R., Xious Divinshield, Y ann RICCI, Y asmin Estrella, Y ezi Goomer, YLF , <br>Y oshiki KUCHIKURA, Yue, Yuu Gamon, Zach Theis, Zach Y okell, Zachary Alvarado, Zachary Knippel, Zachary Longoria, Zachary Stamper, Zack Holmes, Zack Long, Zak and Beth, Zalyn Harper, Zandermoore, Zane <br>Graves, Zasabi, Zeb Berryman, Zev Rothenberg, ZHULUL-N. AZMAN, Zoltam, ZombieGarou, Zsolt Kertay.</p>","markdown":""},"sort":26800000,"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241731,"modifiedTime":1783973241731,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"librarySlug":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed-2022-07-01","category":"Core Book","sourceFile":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf","sourcePath":"C:\\Users\\Gamer\\Documents\\Broken Tales KS [ENG]\\bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf"}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"